data.name: WIC Booneter Expedition
data.desc: WIC sends Jan Gijsbertszoon Booneter to reinforce WIC Pater Expedition, but Booneter is too late for this, and instead takes some ships of Sp Hon flotilla
data.locn: St. Vincent, Cape Tiburon, Havana, Cape San Antonio, Dry Tortugas, Florida Straits, Bahamas, île-à-Vache, Matanzas
data.note:
Inc CC Jol voyage fm Colombia to Yuc, close to Main [reconnoitring?] /v Goslinga [missg] /
 Booneter and Ita thus roamed the Caribbean, each following the traditional procedure of dividing their fleets into several units in order to operate more effectively /v Goslinga 217 /[missg]
